the long silence ( italian : il lungo silenzio , german : zeit des zorns , french : le long silence ) is a 1993 italian-german-french political thriller-drama film directed by margarethe von trotta .   for her performance in this film carla gravina was awarded best actress at the 1993 montreal world film festival and won the italian golden globe for best actress .   the film also won the italian golden globes for best original score and for best screenplay .